========================================================================
WAY 4: H4 REFRACTIONS (K_H4 + gamma_1 = pi/10)
========================================================================

K_H4 derivation:
  K_H4 = Z / M* = 15 / (12/11) = 15 * 11/12 = 55/4
  K_H4 = 13.7500000000  (exact: 55/4 = 13.75)
  Verification: 15*11/12 = 13.7500000000  Match: True

f_H4 (H4 Refraction Correction):
  Derived from v_g = c * M* * (10/pi) * f_H4 * Z = pi*c (for Z=1, M*=12/11)
  Solving: pi = (12/11) * (10/pi) * f_H4  =>  f_H4 = pi^2 * 11/120
  f_H4 = 0.904713736766525
  NOTE: f_H4 = pi^2*11/120 = 0.9047... (NOT 0.8976; prior memo had arithmetic error)
  2*pi/7 = 0.897597901025655  (distinct constant; vertex angle)
  Verify v_g/c = (12/11)*(10/pi)*f_H4 = 3.141592653589793
  pi                                   = 3.141592653589793
  Match (error < 1e-14): True

gamma_1 = pi/10 = 0.314159265358979
  CORRECTION (Lemma 7.6 v1.7): prior M8-series had gamma_1 = pi/12.
  Corrected: gamma_1 = pi/10. This propagates through f_H4 derivation.

4 Physical Predictions from K_H4 = 13.75:
  1. G_eff = G_0 * K_H4 = 13.7500 * G_0  (gravity lensing in Z=15 field)
  2. Delta_tau_H4 = delta/(c/K_H4) = 1.89m / (c/13.75) = 86.6828 ns
  3. Routes max = 35 * K_H4/10 = 35 * 1.375 = 48.125 -> 48 routes
  4. ebits min = 2800/K_H4 = 2800/13.75 = 203.6364 -> 204 ebits

H4 Self-Duality (120-cell <-> 600-cell):
  120-cell: 600 vertices, 1200 edges,  720 faces, 120 cells
  600-cell: 120 vertices,  720 edges, 1200 faces, 600 cells
  Duality map: vertices <-> cells, edges <-> faces (by face count swap)

  Resonator mapping (from M8I/M8L, CERTIFIED):
    120 cells   -> 120 resonator cavities = HEALTH_PASS (M8L 120/120)
    600 vertices -> 600 wormhole mouths (M8I architecture)
    1200 edges  -> 1200 ebit channels (2800/1200 = 2.33 ebits/edge)
    35 routes   -> Bands 1-35 of 108-band Theorem 4.1 spectrum

  M* derivation from H4:
    M* = 600/550 = 12/11  (where 550 = 600 - 600/12 = 600 - 50)
    K_H4 = Z/M* = 15/(12/11) = 15*11/12 = 55/4 = 13.75  (exact)

  Ratio 120-cell/600-cell cells: 120/600 = 1/5
  Ratio 120-cell/600-cell edges: 1200/720 = 5/3

